metadata.name: Night Golf
metadata.description:
A solitary figure stands upon the tee. The harvest moon highlights a small fluttering flag in the distance.

Impossibly far. But she is strong.

Impossible narrow. But her aim is true.

She takes her shot.

---

Edition 1 of 1 'Night Golf' by the NonFungibleGolfClub.
